Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.80,0:24:33.19,DCMain,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.19,0:24:34.91,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Window glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.91,0:24:36.52,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Did you hear from Shinichi \Nabout the school trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.91,0:24:39.91,Don'tMiss,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.52,0:24:37.98,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.98,0:24:39.71,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I need to do something fast.
